OL,3,C'Let my girl's death be a lesson' -
OL,4,CMother's plea after daughter dies from
OL,5,CMDMA
OL,7,FITV News' Jacquie Bird spoke to Debbie
OL,8,Fabout her daughter Lucy's death.
OL,10,FThe grieving mother of a 16-year-old
OL,11,Fgirl from Exmouth who died after
OL,12,Ftaking MDMA, has called on parents to
OL,13,Fshare her daughter's story and talk to
OL,14,Ftheir children about the dangers of
OL,15,Fdrugs.
