OL,3,C'Let my girl's death be a lesson' -
OL,4,CMother's plea after daughter dies from
OL,5,CMDMA
OL,7,FSpeaking to ITV News West Country,
OL,8,FLucy Hill's mother, Debbie, expressed
OL,9,Fher hope that the tragedy would serve
OL,10,Fas a powerful lesson for others, as
OL,11,Ftwo teenage boys were sentenced this
OL,12,Fweek for supplying the drugs that led
OL,13,Fto Lucy's death.
OL,15,F"We had no idea that she would ever
OL,16,Fconsider taking a tablet. We were so
OL,17,Fshocked when we were told she had
OL,18,Ftaken the MDMA," Lucy's mother said.
