OL,3,C'Let my girl's death be a lesson' -
OL,4,CMother's plea after daughter dies from
OL,5,CMDMA
OL,7,F"We know that she was conscious when
OL,8,Fshe was in the ambulance, but by the
OL,9,Ftime she got to hospital she was
OL,10,Funresponsive, so she didn't know we
OL,11,Fwere there waiting for her. That's my
OL,12,Fbiggest regret, that she didn't know
OL,13,Fwe were there."
OL,15,F"Every parent, please have a
OL,16,Fconversation with your son or daughter
OL,17,Fand make them aware of the dangers. I
OL,18,Fhope that nobody ever has to go
OL,19,Fthrough what we have been going
OL,20,Fthrough the last few years and will be
OL,21,Ffor the rest of our lives."
