OL,7,FThe story was shared during the
OL,8,Fsentencing of James Greaves, 19, and
OL,9,FTaylor Rowsell, 18, who were found
OL,10,Fguilty of supplying the drugs that led
OL,11,Fto Lucy's death.
OL,13,FDuring court proceedings, Lucy's
OL,14,Fsister, Chloe, delivered an emotional
OL,15,Fimpact statement about the devastating
OL,16,Floss.
