OL,3,C'Let my girl's death be a lesson' -
OL,4,CMother's plea after daughter dies from
OL,5,CMDMA
OL,7,F"We were just the best of friends; we
OL,8,Fwould never argue, we always knew
OL,9,Fwhere one another was, we were always
OL,10,Fby each other's side. It's just so
OL,11,Fhard to believe that she has gone in
OL,12,Fthe click of a finger," Chloe shared.
OL,14,FLucy, described as a conscientious
OL,15,Fstudent with a love for her friends,
OL,16,Fthe beach, and her younger sister, had
OL,17,Fjust sat a mock exam the day she died
OL,18,Fin November 2022.
