OL,4,CMother's plea after daughter dies from
OL,5,CMDMA
OL,7,FDetective Inspector Sally Johns, from
OL,8,FDevon and Cornwall police emphasised
OL,9,Fthat the real issue is not solely the
OL,10,Fprevalence of drugs, but ensuring that
OL,11,Fyoung people and their families have
OL,12,Fthe right information to make safe
OL,13,Fchoices.
OL,15,F"Lucy was just a normal girl, she went
OL,16,Foff that morning, she sat a mock exam
OL,17,Fand she had a really bright future.
OL,26,@wD@AOU
