OL,3,C'Let my girl's death be a lesson' -
OL,4,CMother's plea after daughter dies from
OL,5,CMDMA
OL,7,F"We have come to realise that it's not
OL,8,Freally about how widespread drugs are,
OL,9,Fit's more about making sure young
OL,10,Fpeople have the right information and
OL,11,Fparents and guardians have the right
OL,12,Finformation," she explained.
OL,14,F"If you are thinking about taking a
OL,15,Fdrug, I really urge you to think
OL,16,Fagain, because we don't know what goes
OL,17,Finto them," she added.
