OL,3,C'Let my girl's death be a lesson' -
OL,4,CMother's plea after daughter dies from
OL,5,CMDMA
OL,7,FExeter Crown Court heard that Greaves
OL,8,Fsupplied the MDMA, commonly known as
OL,9,Fecstasy, to Rowsell, who then sold it
OL,10,Fat a club event targeted at young
OL,11,Fpeople, where no alcohol was served.
OL,13,FRowsell, who was 16 at the time, made
OL,14,Faround #350 selling the tablets to
OL,15,Fpartygoers, including Lucy and her
OL,16,Ffriends.
OL,18,FBoth defendants were minors at the
OL,19,Ftime of the offense and had previously
OL,20,Fadmitted to supplying class A drugs.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G8/9
