OL,3,C'Let my girl's death be a lesson' -
OL,4,CMother's plea after daughter dies from
OL,5,CMDMA
OL,7,FJudge James Adkins sentenced Greaves
OL,8,Fto three-and-a-half years in a young
OL,9,Foffender institution, while Rowsell
OL,10,Freceived a two-year sentence.
OL,12,FThe Hill family hopes that Lucy's
OL,13,Fstory will prevent other families from
OL,14,Ffacing similar devastation.
